      {
        "h3": { "en": "Mount the tube holder", "zh": "安装导管支架" },
        "body": { "en": "Mount it on the top extrusion beside the control board. Its 4 mm socket anchors the fixed end of the Teflon tube.", "zh": "装在控制板旁边的顶部型材上。它的 4 mm 插孔固定特氟龙管的一端。" },
